    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとう。これは……\n渚が考案したホットフルーツティーか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you. This is…\na hot fruit tea that Nagisa created",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_10_03-ngs019.m4a",
      "text": "はい。追加で入れてもらったメニューです\n沢山売れたんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right. The menu I asked to be added to\nIt sold a lot!",
        "id": ""
