      "text": "やっぱりこの前、{user}さんと\n下見に行って良かったです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm really glad I went to do some preliminary visit\nwith {user}-san a while ago",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.1002558865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
