      "text": "寒い時に冷たい飲み物を飲むと想像以上に\n体が冷えちゃうんだって気付けましたから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized that drinking a cold drink in cold weather\nmakes your body colder than you'd think",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.0002558865,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
